    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo-for-github"><a href="#hexo-for-github" class="headerlink" title="hexo for github"></a>hexo for github</h1><h3 id="1-下载"><a href="#1-下载" class="headerlink" title="1.下载"></a>1.下载</h3><ul><li><p>git <a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v6.11.4/node-v6.11.4-x86.msi" target="_blank" rel="external">X86</a>  <a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v6.11.4/node-v6.11.4-x64.msi" target="_blank" rel="external">X64</a></p><p>运行Git Bash验证：<strong> git –version </strong></p></li><li><p>node <a href="https://github.com/git-for-windows/git/releases/download/v2.14.2.windows.3/Git-2.14.2.3-32-bit.exe" target="_blank" rel="external">X86</a>  <a href="https://github.com/git-for-windows/git/releases/download/v2.14.2.windows.3/Git-2.14.2.3-64-bit.exe" target="_blank" rel="external">X64</a></p><p>验证：<strong> node -v </strong> 和 <strong> npm -v </strong></p></li></ul><h3 id="2-注册Github"><a href="#2-注册Github" class="headerlink" title="2.注册Github"></a>2.注册Github</h3><p>  新建仓库：user.github.io</p><h3 id="3-安装-hexo"><a href="#3-安装-hexo" class="headerlink" title="3.安装 hexo"></a>3.安装 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo</a></h3><p>  安装：<strong> npm install hexo-cli -g </strong></p><p>  验证：<strong> hexo version </strong></p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="4-新建项目"><a href="#4-新建项目" class="headerlink" title="4.新建项目"></a>4.新建项目</h3><p>  <strong><br>  hexo init user.github.io<br>  cd user.github.io<br>  npm install   </strong></p><p>  检验：<strong> hexo server </strong>或者<strong> hexo s </strong> 然后访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:4000</a></p><h3 id="5-关联Github和Hexo"><a href="#5-关联Github和Hexo" class="headerlink" title="5.关联Github和Hexo"></a>5.关联Github和Hexo</h3><ul><li><p>生成SSH-Key：<strong> ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “user@email.com” </strong>输入密码或为空，会生成”C:\users\user.ssh\id_rsa.pub”文件，打开复制全部内容，打开<a href="https://github.com/settings/ssh" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/settings/ssh</a>新建new SSH Key粘贴进去就好。</p></li><li><p>检验：<strong> ssh -T git@github.com </strong>选择yes看到欢迎语就好了</p></li><li><p>配置Git个人信息</p><p>用户名：<strong> git config –global user.name “user” </strong></p><p>邮箱：<strong> git config –global user.email “email” </strong></p><p>配置Deployment，修改文件夹里的 _config.yml文件最后（注：冒号后面有个空格）</p><p><strong><br>deploy:<br>type: git<br>repo: git@github.com:user/user.github.io.git<br>branch: master</strong></p></li></ul><h3 id="6-本地文件提交到GitHub"><a href="#6-本地文件提交到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="6.本地文件提交到GitHub"></a>6.本地文件提交到GitHub</h3><p>  <strong><br>  npm install hexo-deployer-git –save //安装部署插件<br>  hexo clean //生成新的 public文件<br>  hexo generate //生成新的 public文件<br>  hexo deploy //部署  </strong></p><h3 id="7-Hexo基本操作"><a href="#7-Hexo基本操作" class="headerlink" title="7.Hexo基本操作"></a>7.Hexo基本操作</h3><ul><li><p>新建文章: <strong> hexo new “new post” </strong> 可以到其目录编辑 .md 文件，也可以直接在所在的文件夹创建 .md 文件。</p></li><li><p>文章抬头：</p><p><strong><br>title: hexo for github<br>date: 2017-10-17 16:29:05<br>description: How to make a blog #文章描述<br>categories: #文章分类<br>- 笔记<br>tags: #文章标签<br>- Github<br>- Hexo<br>toc: true # 生成目录<br>author: yyh0301<br>comments:<br>original:<br>permalink: #指定链接</strong></p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
